{"tid":2151361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭評分又跌 5成人畀0分 平均民望再成歷任四特首中最低","createTime":"2020-08-11T10:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T14:32:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":263,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"827c73e6ae521fd29904caeeec23bc774200a18e","tid":2151361,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:51:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/FX4QZI5K4QAQF273AXYGMO3WTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FFX4QZI5K4QAQF273AXYGMO3WTA%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=d1c9ac0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FFX4QZI5K4QAQF273AXYGMO3WTA%2F&h=1b117e3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/FX4QZI5K4QAQF273AXYGMO3WTA/</a><br />\n<br />\n就在政商界傳出北京欲「折磨」港人讓林鄭連任特首之時，香港民意研究所今日（11日）公佈新一輪特區政府民望數字，林鄭民望評分持續下跌，僅得26.9分，當中近5成市民給予0分；而律政司司長鄭若驊評分略微升至22.2分，是繼2019年6月後的新高，惟仍是3位司長中民望評分最低。香港民研亦綜合歷次調查數字，發現林鄭目前的平均民望僅得43.3分，再次成為歷任4位特首中平均民望最低的一位。至於平均民望最高的特首則為曾蔭權首輪任期的66.1分，其次為董建華首輪任期的55.8分。"},{"pid":"20d9fbd2ff55497268ae58559f4cf83794bfeb2f","tid":2151361,"uid":231583,"like":101,"dislike":4,"score":97,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:52:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a4257c7f4c9a161c68f137a7c578758afea4ea4","tid":2151361,"uid":132587,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:53:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebfbb5048267f8f2353cb7f82b1c66f823c08d83","tid":2151361,"uid":68553,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"咁都唔洗炒,真係奇蹟"},{"pid":"559d533770740d75a9abfb2035e66beea0d11666","tid":2151361,"uid":43062,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:57:39.000Z","msg":"竟然仲有得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdd7eacc047eb9bb423cc7342a9e79683746625","tid":2151361,"uid":47311,"l